{"tid":1859423,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】中國海外維權人士宣佈「武漢獨立」 批混亂局面源於非民選政府","createTime":"2020-02-03T08:42:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-03T09:35:20.000Z","uid":70063,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b006713a9f2cef2ed0ef9eaa1abbfa31677e027e","tid":1859423,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎全國大爆發，當中湖北武漢更成為重災區，確診病例逾1.1萬宗。旅居加拿大的海外民運組織「民主中國陣線」主席盛雪昨日在網上發表成立「武漢臨時政府」，召集18歲以上武漢居民，參與民選議會及行政首腦。<br />\n<br />\n盛雪在網上發帖指出，武漢警方上月1日「依法處理」8名在網上透露疫情的醫生，湖北官員不僅輕描淡寫疫情，還否認早已出現人傳人的情況，瞞報、打壓，最終失控倉促封城，之後又再出現防護裝備匱乏耗盡、紅十字會和慈善總會弊案頻傳等，混亂源於政府非民選、言論不自由。恰如1946年，中國共產黨黨報《新華日報》社論的斷言：「一黨專制，遍地是災。」<br />\n<br />\n盛雪提出，「今日，2020年02月02日，我們一群血性武漢人，為奪回民權，再造共和，效仿辛亥革命武昌起義的先驅，在此鄭重宣告成立武漢臨時政府，宣佈武漢獨立，湖北獨立！」<br />\n<br />\n盛雪隨後再發帖，參與武漢臨時政府的全體成員，皆為志願奉獻人士，效仿去年10月4日，有香港示威者提出的《香港臨時政府宣言》的內容，宣誓在武漢臨時政府結束、權力移交給民選政府之後，終身不再擔任任何公職。<br />\n<br />\n發帖又指，以武漢臨時政府下命令，即日起所有武漢市的官員、湖北省的官員，脫離共產黨的指揮，通過公開或秘密渠道向本臨時政府報到，看守現有崗位職責，服從本臨時政府的指令，並靜候改組。武漢臨時政府宣告，即日起本臨時政府開始運作，籌組國事會議，籌擬武漢臨時約法，籌辦由全體年滿18歲武漢居民、湖北居民參與投票的普選，建立民選議會和行政首腦。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200203/TFFDDFEJKLMTTXFRVZ2TCMIKOM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0B2SPVi1pSbOZyG1iaSrOerg6jnjT9rjflK8JuIZHpnAScvgv_ZXt8lpc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200203%2FTFFDDFEJKLMTTXFRVZ2TCMIKOM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0B2SPVi1pSbOZyG1iaSrOerg6jnjT9rjflK8JuIZHpnAScvgv_ZXt8lpc&d=sSzAGq%2B8hAhXqg0aovu9KTKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=f1070286\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200203%2FTFFDDFEJKLMTTXFRVZ2TCMIKOM%2F%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR0B2SPVi1pSbOZyG1iaSrOerg6jnjT9rjflK8JuIZHpnAScvgv_ZXt8lpc&h=004fc0ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200203/TFFDDFEJKLMTTXFRVZ2TCMIKOM/?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR0B2SPVi1pSbOZyG1iaSrOerg6jnjT9rjflK8JuIZHpnAScvgv_ZXt8lpc</a>"},{"pid":"90b0ad8ef57d354d0fae5109ab2cbd21c5dcf460","tid":1859423,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T08:54:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1b95391a0620e6e7ab5839c4c94741776cf9096","tid":1859423,"uid":142656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"推大力啲"},{"pid":"b1398b0f21154981f153066cf91a8caed1c42028","tid":1859423,"uid":142656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:22:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b90efb6724ae46065b2831ec769a88348e7e11a","tid":1859423,"uid":117892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:24:03.000Z","msg":"時代革命"},{"pid":"fb7b575f4341ff1d1ecedbd93e7c22c2664a7098","tid":1859423,"uid":262093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dec8e3f4b42840ab98266327094d641fa8c24b1b","tid":1859423,"uid":252321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"5c1b2b70081732ee2e5d568a5d26abb886d996e9","tid":1859423,"uid":288360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:32:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">推大力啲<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"ab3b36a2d63a32629c025cfe27fe0ce7533c56bf","tid":1859423,"uid":67551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T09:35:20.000Z","msg":"<img sr